                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020714-12-defend172 t18020714-12-punish69"></join>
               Confined twelve months in Newgate
            </rs>, and <rs id="t18020714-12-punish70" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18020714-12-punish70" type="punishmentCategory" value="corporal"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18020714-12-punish70" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="publicWhipping"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020714-12-defend172 t18020714-12-punish70"></join>
               publicly whipped
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>London Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
